Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.-90,0:00:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inherited will...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.64,0:00:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The tide of the times...\NPeople's dreams...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.54,0:00:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These things cannot be stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.38,0:00:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as people seek\Nthe answer of freedom,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.48,0:00:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,these things will never cease to be!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.03,0:00:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only believe in the future--\NI don't care if anyone laughs
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.20,0:00:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That racing passion makes you shine
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.54,0:00:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too bright, but I want to gaze at it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.54,0:00:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sense "aesthetics" somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.15,0:00:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really, really stuck on you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.55,0:00:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I follow, follow in the footsteps\Nof a dream that resembles no one
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.99,0:00:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until I dramatically get it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.33,0:01:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe In Wonderland!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.14,0:01:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to catch, catch the shape\Nof a dream no one can see
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.44,0:01:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to go with you,\Nso passionate feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.58,0:01:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really need\Neverything to add up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.59,0:01:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather than run-of-the-mill daily life,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.76,0:01:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,run for paradise instead
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.36,0:01:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe In Wonderland!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.71,0:01:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing, old guy?!\NMove this rock!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.98,0:01:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect timing!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.65,0:01:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing here, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.25,0:01:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the deal, Nami?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.95,0:01:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dinosaur!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.75,0:02:00.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's someone on this island!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.83,0:02:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.84,0:02:18.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.28,0:02:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,10,000 Kilogram Press!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.35,0:02:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. 3. Please excuse the codename.\NI'm a mere formative artist.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.29,0:02:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And this is my realist painter assistant,\NMiss Golden Week.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.83,0:02:37.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. 3?! The Wax-Wax Fruit man?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.10,0:02:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a "candle man" who controls\Nthe wax he secretes from his body.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.74,0:02:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are gonna pay for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.66,0:03:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Devilish Candle!\NTears of Regret and Tears of Anger"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.81,0:03:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Curse you! What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.25,0:03:29.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.88,0:03:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is why I can't stand\Nunsophisticated dolts.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.62,0:03:41.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm creating a work of art, obviously.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.13,0:03:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just be a good little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.13,0:03:53.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you honestly think you\Ncould escape from Baroque Works?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.88,0:04:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Especially when someone with a\N30 million-Berry bounty winds up like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.08,0:04:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy I could thank them\Nfor what happened at Whisky Peak.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.45,0:04:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wannabe pirates should\Nnever have stuck your noses
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.32,0:04:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,into such delicate issues as this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.16,0:04:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've already captured your\Nswordsman friend and the other girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.26,0:04:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You caught Zoro?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.83,0:04:23.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you guys're gonna get cut down!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.74,0:04:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.77,0:04:26.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You still talk big,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.84,0:04:29.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even after one of my\NKicky Bombs to the face?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.01,0:04:32.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't hurt me with that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.11,0:04:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna kick you guys' asses!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.75,0:04:46.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.16,0:04:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.60,0:04:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.92,0:05:12.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Fool!\N--Luffy-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.65,0:05:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-san! Luffy-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.92,0:05:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Miss Valentine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.59,0:05:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.62,0:05:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp-san! Karoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.78,0:05:43.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.38,0:05:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it up! Give it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.78,0:05:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once solidified,\Nmy Candle Jacket is as hard as iron!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.06,0:05:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You giants may have brutish strength,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.46,0:05:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it becomes all but useless\Nonce you've been caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.63,0:06:01.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Using your brain is the key.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.87,0:06:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to\Nuselessly face you head-on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.70,0:06:08.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You lowered your guard\Nas you reveled in victory,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.61,0:06:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Red Ogre Broggy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.88,0:06:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't glare at me like that.\NYou're terrifying me so!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.92,0:06:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should be happy! Your long,\Nlong battle has come to an end!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.92,0:06:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fought for a whole century\Nfor your so-called pride, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.43,0:06:32.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't the taste of victory\Nbe especially sweet, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.13,0:06:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it is the fruit\Nof others' assistance...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.04,0:06:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.67,0:06:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you! You don't mean to say...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.68,0:06:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the final victory belongs to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.38,0:06:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you aware that the large\Nbounties on your heads from long ago
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.75,0:06:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,come to 200 million Berries total?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.49,0:06:59.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even today this holds true!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.36,0:07:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.39,0:07:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel as if I've discovered\Na long-lost treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.50,0:07:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's what you're after, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.37,0:07:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. 3!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.60,0:07:12.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We brought her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.44,0:07:14.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our company's little traitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.34,0:07:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What took so long?\NI was getting sick of waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.08,0:07:20.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your methods are too underhanded, Mr. 3!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.61,0:07:23.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Planting bombs in Dorry-san's alcohol...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.45,0:07:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.25,0:07:27.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alcohol?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.05,0:07:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The alcohol I gave him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.42,0:07:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dorry! How was your drink?!\NHit the spot, didn't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.33,0:07:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... It tasted "godly"...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.37,0:07:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what you meant, Dorry?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.34,0:07:48.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wretched little girl,\Ngiving our tricks away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.34,0:07:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, no matter.\NThere's nothing you can do now, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.01,0:07:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Candle...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.82,0:08:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Lock!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.06,0:08:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. 5!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.63,0:08:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring the swordsman and the girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.96,0:08:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're about to begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.84,0:08:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Extra Big Candle Set!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.48,0:09:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-This is Mr. 3's ability?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.02,0:09:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.02,0:09:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.00,0:09:19.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How naive.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.97,0:09:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Being ridiculed by people of\Ntheir caliber is so embarrassing
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.97,0:09:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that I'm pissed at myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.64,0:09:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't help that you're weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.41,0:09:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.98,0:09:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing! Just set\Nthe candles up quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.31,0:09:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Set?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.72,0:09:38.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.95,0:09:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san... Mr. Bushido...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.55,0:09:45.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vivi! What happened?!\NWeren't you with Luffy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.29,0:09:46.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I was, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.99,0:09:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're wondering about Straw Hat,\NI took care of him myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.43,0:09:55.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was an easy job, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.30,0:10:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.30,0:10:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome, friends, to my service set!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.92,0:10:56.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this how it feels to be\Na candle stuck in a cake?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.60,0:11:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that spinning thing up there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.20,0:11:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I can't move my legs...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.30,0:11:07.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course they're not gonna let us move.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.37,0:11:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.34,0:11:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn. It's hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.91,0:11:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus I can't put any strength\Ninto it from this stance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.92,0:11:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something's raining down!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.45,0:11:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May you enjoy my "Candle Service"!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.06,0:11:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The wax haze falling from above you
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.79,0:11:32.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will eventually change\Nyou into wax figures!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.23,0:11:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll become perfect "human models"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.70,0:11:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that not even I could\Nachieve with my skills!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.04,0:11:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your wax figures will have\Nliterally captured your spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.38,0:11:49.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now die, in the name of art.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.11,0:11:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Screw that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.72,0:11:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do we have to turn\Ninto your works of art?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.92,0:11:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Broggy-san! Quit sitting\Nthere and go on a rampage!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.76,0:12:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna get turned into\Na wax figure too, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.46,0:12:04.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, talk about a huge person...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.13,0:12:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anything you say to him is pointless!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.47,0:12:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He just now realized he foolishly\Nshed proud, joyful tears of victory
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.37,0:12:18.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,after killing his friend Dorry,\Nwith whom he fought for 100 years,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.84,0:12:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but without even noticing that he\Nhad suffered injuries beforehand!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.78,0:12:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or did you perhaps cry\Nfor your friend, instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.92,0:12:38.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever the case, there's no\Nundoing what you've done now, fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.94,0:12:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.84,0:12:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.98,0:12:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From the moment we\Nfirst exchanged blows...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.78,0:13:02.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I knew Dorry was hiding something.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.39,0:13:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You knew, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.86,0:13:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.26,0:13:09.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If so, then why didn't\Nyou cease your fighting?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.06,0:13:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't see a shred of pity in\Nthe way you heartily cut him down!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.34,0:13:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A pipsqueak who doesn't even\Nknow the first thing about duels
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.04,0:13:24.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,would never understand\Nthe meaning of those tears!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.94,0:13:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What would you know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.55,0:13:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying I should shame a warrior
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.02,0:13:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who hides the fact he's been\Nweakened and tries to fight anyway?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.02,0:13:44.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A warrior who'll go that far to\Nkeep fighting doesn't deserve pity!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.56,0:13:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now... I know the reason behind it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.57,0:13:56.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I know, I'm going to\Nfinish things with my own two hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.98,0:14:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the very least I can\Ndo for my dear friend Dorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.99,0:14:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Broggy-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.40,0:14:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Broggy-san!\N--Broggy-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.77,0:14:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What an annoying, talkative monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.45,0:14:36.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Usopp...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.98,0:14:41.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.69,0:14:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you let them get away with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.36,0:14:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.00,0:15:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you... not stand this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.18,0:15:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Let's all three of us\Ngo beat them senseless!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.02,0:15:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Broggy-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.19,0:15:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dumb!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.26,0:15:24.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I underestimated how brutishly\Nstrong these giants can be!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.23,0:15:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would seem you need\Nto be seized completely!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.93,0:15:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wax-Wax Arts! Handcuffs!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.07,0:15:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just getting started!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.95,0:15:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now for the finishing touch!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.42,0:15:52.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.39,0:16:03.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't move now, can you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.57,0:16:08.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can he be so horrific?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.84,0:16:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then! Accelerate, Candle Service!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.18,0:16:20.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn these people into wax figures!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.65,0:16:23.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-My chest is starting to hurt...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.46,0:16:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The wax haze is getting into our lungs!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.79,0:16:30.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, we're going to turn\Ninto wax figures from the inside out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.26,0:16:35.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Yes! Make it look like\Nyou're in as much pain as you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.60,0:16:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Expressions of pain and agony\Nare the very things I seek in art!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.01,0:16:44.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May you solidify\Nwhile filled with terror!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.44,0:16:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You call this art,\Nyou creepy topknot freak?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.11,0:16:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you do that to Broggy-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.12,0:16:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are going to\Nregret this! You got that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.29,0:17:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scream and holler all you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.30,0:17:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For 100 years...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.14,0:17:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...day in and day out,\Nwe fought and fought...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.98,0:17:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and dueled only because of our\Npride of Elbaf, village of warriors!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.72,0:17:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet... why are we being subjected\Nto this, Elbaf, god of war?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.83,0:17:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this is how we're\Nto meet our end, Elbaf...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.93,0:17:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...don't you think it's unfair?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.17,0:17:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why won't you let us die in battle?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.74,0:17:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a look!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.94,0:17:54.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! That sorrow!\NThat grief! That struggle!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.35,0:17:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a marvelous work of art!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.82,0:18:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Elbaf!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.05,0:18:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! My hands won't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.89,0:18:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna die this way!\NCan't we do something?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.39,0:18:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My body's already turning stiff!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.49,0:18:10.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do we do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.09,0:18:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro! Do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.56,0:18:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.60,0:18:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can still move, can't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.90,0:18:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So can I.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.11,0:18:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whadya say we crush these guys together?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.78,0:18:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on, Zoro! What are you doing?!\NYou're not seriously gonna--!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.58,0:18:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.32,0:18:33.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna cut your own legs?!\NQuit joking around!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.79,0:18:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no joke.\NIt's the only way out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.09,0:18:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you two gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.09,0:18:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?!\NIt's pointless!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.63,0:18:43.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you do get down from here\Nthat way, they'll catch you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.56,0:18:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way to\Nknow that unless we try!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.03,0:18:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna kick the bucket\Nif we stay here anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.03,0:18:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's put up some ugly struggling!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.04,0:18:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no reason to die heroically\Nfor these pieces of scum!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.47,0:18:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.71,0:19:00.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell? Is he crazy?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.45,0:19:04.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's bluffing!\NThere's no way he could do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.15,0:19:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's merely acting tough!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.92,0:19:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a cheeky runt.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.46,0:19:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pathetic. It seems I had\Neven lost the will to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.13,0:19:25.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll fight alongside you\Nand your fighting spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.20,0:19:27.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't be serious, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.34,0:19:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How will you be able\Nto fight afterward?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.57,0:19:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.08,0:19:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... I plan to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.65,0:19:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are these guys?!\NThey're off their rocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.42,0:19:41.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of man is he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.15,0:19:45.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I've seen this\Nlook somewhere before...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.19,0:19:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Vivi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.06,0:19:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you prepared not to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.03,0:19:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait! I'll fight, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.56,0:19:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Vivi!\N--Alright, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.00,0:19:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it, runt!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.37,0:20:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be stupid!\NWhat can you possibly do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.62,0:20:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.78,0:20:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna kick your asses,\Njust so you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.12,0:20:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.09,0:20:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Let's do it, Usopp!\N--Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.76,0:20:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bird!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.56,0:20:26.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.63,0:20:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Karoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.77,0:20:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master Broggy!\NWe've taken on your frustration!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.77,0:20:32.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.87,0:20:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beat those guys up so much\Nthey lose their original forms
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.34,0:20:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and send them flying far off somewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.81,0:20:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.71,0:20:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These guys spoiled\Nthe old giant guys' duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.98,0:20:48.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're the one with the\Nhighest bounty in the East Blue?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.59,0:20:51.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My, how Navy Headquarters'\Nstandards have fallen!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.46,0:20:53.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Whoa! What a weird head!\N--Quiet, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.93,0:20:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--It's the number 3, and it's on fire!\N--Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.43,0:20:59.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Break this pillar first, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.26,0:21:02.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're about to turn into wax figures!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.00,0:21:04.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? You're in trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.44,0:21:06.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, there was no problem at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.64,0:21:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Your leg!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.11,0:21:11.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I went about\Nhalfway through, I'd say.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.11,0:21:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is that no problem at all?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.45,0:21:18.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For now, could you bust\Nthis pillar for us, Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.75,0:21:20.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I leave the rest to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.95,0:21:23.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, no problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.45,0:21:25.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't be so sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.76,0:21:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dunno what it is,\Nbut let's break that thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.03,0:21:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.46,0:21:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a bit of a different person today!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.03,0:21:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry it up! We're gonna solidify!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.77,0:21:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world is awfully big
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.24,0:21:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so even if there is treasure somewhere,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.55,0:21:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the odds are astronomical
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.95,0:21:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So relying on dumb luck\Nwon't get you anywhere
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.09,0:22:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So even...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.89,0:22:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...if someone stops me or\Nlaughs at me from the shadows
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.63,0:22:11.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the ship will continue forward
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.84,0:22:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bon voyage!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.94,0:22:15.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget about them!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.24,0:22:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know I'm a fool, but I gotta go
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.95,0:22:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The crazier the dream,\Nthe cooler the ambition
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.62,0:22:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know I'm a fool, but I'm gonna fight
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.29,0:22:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The farther the sea,\Nthe more heavenly it surely is
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.30,0:22:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do everything you can, and you'll\Nget a little nearer to any horizon
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.25,0:22:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum Mallet!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.98,0:22:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! The pillar broke!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.82,0:23:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Why didn't you run away?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.99,0:23:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.25,0:23:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The wax has us stuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.45,0:23:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's why?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.92,0:23:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and break this set!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.39,0:23:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.26,0:23:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit joking and hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.96,0:23:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?\NI don't feel like saving you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.00,0:23:13.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.30,0:23:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"A Hex on Luffy! Colors Trap"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.17,0:23:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
